## Color Coding Visualization

Ogni tipo di recupero ha un colore:
- **Recupero:** ğŸ”µ Blue (#3b82f6)
- **Potenziamento:** ğŸŸ¢ Green (#10b981)
- **Sportello:** ğŸŸ  Orange (#f59e0b)
- **Corso:** ğŸ”´ Red (#ef4444)

### Default/Compact:
```
â”ƒ Recupero     â†’  background: #3b82f620, border-left: 3px solid #3b82f6
â”ƒ Potenziamentoâ†’  background: #10b98120, border-left: 3px solid #10b981
```

### Cards/Modern:
```
â”ƒ Recupero     â†’  background: #3b82f620, border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6
â”ƒ              â†’  + Tag icon in Cards
â”ƒ              â†’  + Gradient in Modern
```

### Modern Gradient Example:
```
Linear gradient from color15 to color05:
linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f615, #3b82f605)
+ backdrop-blur-sm
+ border-white/20
= Glass effect with subtle color tint
```

