## Responsive Behavior

### Mobile (<768px):
All variants stack vertically with reduced horizontal spacing.
Recommended: `default` or `minimal` for best mobile UX.

### Tablet (768-1024px):
All variants work well. Grid maintains 5-column layout.

### Desktop (1024-1920px):
Optimal range for all variants.

### Large Screen (>1920px):
- `compact` shines (all 10 modules + more visible)
- `minimal` might feel too spacious
- `modern` scales beautifully with gradients

---

